KISS-serv - A KISS repository for mail and git servers
________________________________________________________________________________

This is subject to heavy future modification, but this is roughly all you need
to copy what I have going on to host most of the infrastructure behind KISS!

For information on how exactly to set all these cool bits and bobs up, you can
find more information at my own personal blog:
https://dilyn-corner.github.io/blog/Server-Mail
